    "en": {
      "title": "Yupun becomes first South Asian to finish 100m below 10 seconds & win",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st);\u00a0Yupun Abeykon managed to become the first ever Sri Lankan and the South Asian to break the 10-second barrier for the very first time in the 100m category.",
        "Abeykoon earlier entered the finals of the 100m A category of the Resisprint International Chaux-de-Fonds 2022 in Switzerland, finished the event with a time of 9.96 seconds.",
        "Accordingly, today he broke the record he set last May by recording a time of 10.6 seconds.",
        "Yupun becomes first South Asian to finish 100m below 10 seconds & win"
      ],
